---
description: Use shadcn/ui skill before editing GodMode web UI
alwaysApply: true
priority: 25
---
Before editing React UI in apps/web, call use_skill('shadcn-ui') and follow shadcn/ui conventions.

Use existing @/components/ui components, semantic color tokens, FieldGroup + Field for forms, and flex gap-* for spacing (not space-y-*).
